{"tid":104771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特 朗 普 威  脅 出 兵  墨西哥","createTime":"2017-02-02T10:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T14:05:02.000Z","uid":62257,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"147d8b4dfb84b67d414878e955e3ad4e23883c7d","tid":104771,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E5%87%BA%E5%85%B5%E5%B0%8D%E4%BB%98%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5%E5%A2%83%E5%85%A7-%E5%A3%9E%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90-060000409.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2584%2585%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2585%25B5%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25BB%2598%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%2593%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E5%2585%25A7-%25E5%25A3%259E%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25AD%2590-060000409.html&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=58dcdc53\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E5%87%BA%E5%85%B5%E5%B0%8D%E4%BB%98%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5%E5%A2%83%E5%85%A7-%E5%A3%9E%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90-060000409.html</a><br />\n【星島日報報道】美國總統特朗普上周五與墨西哥總統涅托通電話時再度口出狂言，要求涅托採取行動對付墨西哥境內的「壞分子」。如果墨西哥甚麼都不做的話，美國便會派軍越境進入墨國境內去對付他們。<br />\n　　消息人士透露，特朗普和涅托共進行了長達一小時通話。美聯社記者取得部分對話的內容，顯示特朗普發出這番威脅。白宮和墨西哥政府均作出否認。<br />\n　　《紐約郵報》報道，根據記者取得的部分通話紀錄，特朗普說：「你們(墨西哥)下面有一堆壞分子。你們在制止他們方面做得不夠，我猜你們的軍隊怕了他們。我們的軍隊不怕，因此我可能會派他們(美軍)過去對付他們。」<br />\n　　特朗普在過往的場合中都說過「壞分子」這個字眼，通常是指墨西哥的毒裊和犯法的偷渡者。即時未知道涅托作出甚麼回應。<br />\n　　墨西哥記者埃斯特韋斯周三接受當地新聞網站 Aristegui Noticias 訪問時，也提到那次電話通話。他引述特朗普對涅托說：「我不需要墨西哥人，我不需要墨西哥。我們要建牆，你們要付錢，不管你們喜歡不喜歡。」"},{"pid":"519a5511cf057d803e766baf286a703710c97e3e","tid":104771,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:58:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da106c97f3feef3659e995d2559cbc4f146a972e","tid":104771,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:59:38.000Z","msg":"我諗墨西哥人全部帶路，齊齊變美國人"},{"pid":"e8e5aed7fa02fc6460824c435deba8b88c8eef3a","tid":104771,"uid":9185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa71232bbba50c04de76a4fef8cc49f8fe57828","tid":104771,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca194b1c48b8d4b7d8968900318320a85e42b16","tid":104771,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:03:48.000Z","msg":"呢條友真是痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a61ebc4e71862dbe296dbed106a0bb3262c2d6b","tid":104771,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:05:03.000Z","msg":"唔好鳩撐 trump<br />\neven比你核平墨西哥，又有幾多着數？<br />\n<br />\n夠 Isis, PRC 有價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24946bbc9bd1b09573d3c879a3fafecdef56f40e","tid":104771,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:06:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀解攞U？"},{"pid":"0a452d27b63a09c35a8a752ea47710ba5caeb610","tid":104771,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗墨西哥人全部帶路，齊齊變美國人</blockquote><br />\ntrump就是唔比你班老墨做美國人"},{"pid":"5ee3b119f768e81e8377d4f04530d36149b3dba1","tid":104771,"uid":36817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:31:11.000Z","msg":"內文邊到有威脅"},{"pid":"9b687609b86dafbfcb9377776b21bbe6d4cbc11f","tid":104771,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:47:52.000Z","msg":"要